snippet.title: A Smart... MUG?! - Take apart a Heated Thermos!
snippet.description:
YouTubes new channel!: https://www.youtube.com/yt/unboxed for the latest unboxings from YouTubes creators! Good gift ideas for everyone on your list. 
Winter is coming, and this smart mug is designed to keep your drinks warm on the go, or all day long at your desk! This new mug from Ember is the smart mug you never though you needed, but now want to have. http://amzn.to/2zC9VFE

The camera I used to film this video: http://amzn.to/2p7GtkX
The Lens I used for this video: http://amzn.to/1QOXDw2
Wide angle lens: http://amzn.to/2qiYM4u
And this Metabones adapter: http://amzn.to/2iZ67Ty
This is the drone I use: http://amzn.to/2joH00G
